item.title: CVE-2019-10158|2024-08-04T22:10:09.999Z -- red%20hat -- infinispan
item.description: A flaw was found in Infinispan through version 9.4.14.Final. An improper implementation of the session fixation protection in the Spring Session integration can result in incorrect session handling.
